### **NODE 1: Webhook Trigger**
```
Type: Webhook
Method: POST
Path: /generate-preview
Response: Immediately

Expected Input:
{
  "business_name": "Mario's Pizza",
  "business_type": "Restaurant",
  "location": {
    "city": "Brooklyn",
    "state": "NY",
    "address": "123 Main St"
  },
  "services": ["Dine-in", "Delivery", "Catering"],
  "contact": {
    "phone": "555-1234",
    "email": "info@mariospizza.com"
  },
  "tone": "friendly"
}
```

